      <a href="https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/story20210702-1163692" target="_blank"><img class="view-mobile lazyload " data-src alt pinger-seen="true" src="https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/china/undefined" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></a>
    
